OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fairline removes disabled   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fteenager                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, India's aviation minister has said he  
OL,6, is investigating a domestic airline    
OL,7, after it allegedly refused to let a    
OL,8, disabled teenager board its flight.    
OL,10,FThe airline's staff told the teenager's
OL,11,Fparents that he was a risk to other    
OL,12,Fpassengers.                            
OL,14,FThe incident sparked widespread outrage
OL,15,Fwith many calling out the airline for  
OL,16,Fdiscriminatory behaviour.              
OL,18,FIndiGo has denied the allegations,     
OL,19,Fsaying it prides itself on being an    
OL,20,Finclusive organisation.                
